      <odd id="aspace_a8511725ccb5e6432956af019bc55ccc">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 5-D (YRG 5-D), Investment and insurance records of Yale University.</p>  
      </odd>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_5e3b103511b1562833b1aa7fe4de361e">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the records is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.  Files restricted to the office of origin only have been redacted from the finding aid.</p>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_5b167aaff44f497495d1d1599b51cd2a">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Insurance Office, Yale University, Records (RU 531). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_c734ccd10091102bffa7b4e5cff367b3">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_f43eadb819c4917cc54bd2f33e933559">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, policies, statements, accident and injury reports, certificates of insurance, payment statements, and printed materials documenting the activities and operations of the Yale Insurance Office.</p>
         <p>This finding aid contains redacted content. Unredacted version available to office of origin only.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
